      <title>日元观察人士问，随着货币贬值加速，日本将何去何从？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/usd-jpy-yen-watchers-ask-where-is-japan-intervention-as-currency-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元已大幅下跌，跌破了日本的红线，其跌幅让交易员询问当局何时可能开始购买日元以支撑日元——以及为什么他们还没有这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/usd-jpy-yen-watchers-ask-where-is-japan-intervention-as-currency-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在取消印度一周后，马斯克出人意料地访问中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克周日对中国进行了一次未经宣布的访问，而就在一周前，他推迟了对印度的访问，以解决他所说的该汽车制造商面临的紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东南亚热浪导致学校停课，引发电力需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾宣布将停止公立学校的面授课程，而泰国的电力需求则升至创纪录水平，因为席卷南亚的热浪继续造成损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
