    <item>
      <title>极端高温引发警告，泰国电力需求创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thai-power-demand-hits-record-as-extreme-heat-prompts-warnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全国气温飙升，泰国周六用电量飙升至创纪录水平，促使当局在与高温相关的死亡人数不断上升的情况下多次发布健康警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thai-power-demand-hits-record-as-extreme-heat-prompts-warnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:10:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁安德烈·古里耶夫 (Andrey Guryev) 在英国法庭与老朋友因 PhosAgro 股份发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/russian-billionaire-andrey-guryev-sued-in-uk-over-phosagro-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到制裁的俄罗斯亿万富翁安德烈·古里耶夫(Andrey Guryev)与一位朋友因持有全球最大化肥生产商之一的股份而发生的争执在伦敦的一场纠纷中暴露无遗，这场纠纷涉及苏联解体后达成的所谓交易以及在啤酒上做出的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/russian-billionaire-andrey-guryev-sued-in-uk-over-phosagro-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
